936
01:00:09,960 --> 01:00:10,620
 Bože moj,

937
01:00:10,620 --> 01:00:11,420
 ni slava oče.

938
01:00:11,420 --> 01:00:12,200
 A i moramo...

939
01:00:12,200 --> 01:00:16,880
 Oče naš koji jesi na nebesima,

940
01:00:16,880 --> 01:00:18,420
 sveti se ime tvoje,

941
01:00:18,420 --> 01:00:19,980
 dođi kraljestvo tvoje,

942
01:00:19,980 --> 01:00:21,200
 budi volja tvoja,

943
01:00:21,200 --> 01:00:22,080
 kako na nebu,

944
01:00:22,080 --> 01:00:23,200
 tako i na zemlji.

945
01:00:23,780 --> 01:00:26,340
 Ruh naša daj nam danas,

946
01:00:26,340 --> 01:00:28,020
 pusti nama duge naše,

947
01:00:28,020 --> 01:00:30,580
 kako i mi otpuštamo dužnicima našim

948
01:00:30,580 --> 01:00:32,160
 i ne uvedi nas u napast,

949
01:00:32,160 --> 01:00:33,620
 nego i zbavi nas od dva.

950
01:00:33,620 --> 01:00:34,540
 E sad idemo.

951
01:00:34,540 --> 01:00:35,480
 Zdravo Mariju,

952
01:00:35,480 --> 01:00:36,460
 milosti puna,

953
01:00:36,460 --> 01:00:37,560
 gospodin s tobom,

954
01:00:37,560 --> 01:00:39,360
 blagoslovljena ti među ženama

955
01:00:39,360 --> 01:00:41,660
 i blagoslovljen plod uprobe tvoje,

956
01:00:41,660 --> 01:00:42,280
 Isus,

957
01:00:42,280 --> 01:00:44,100
 sveta Mariju,

958
01:00:44,100 --> 01:00:44,600
 majko,

959
01:00:44,600 --> 01:00:47,640
 moji za nas grešnike,

960
01:00:47,640 --> 01:00:49,860
 sada i na času smrti naše,

961
01:00:49,860 --> 01:00:50,260
 amen.

962
01:00:50,260 --> 01:00:51,440
 I sad skupa,

963
01:00:51,440 --> 01:00:53,000
 slava Otcu

964
01:00:53,000 --> 01:00:54,240
 i sinu

965
01:00:54,240 --> 01:00:55,860
 i duhu svetom.

966
01:00:55,860 --> 01:00:59,540
 Tako i sad,

967
01:00:59,540 --> 01:01:01,180
 tako i sada i razda

968
01:01:01,180 --> 01:01:02,880
 i u vijeke vijekova.

969
01:01:02,880 --> 01:01:04,200
 E, ali ti sam im rekao

970
01:01:04,200 --> 01:01:05,580
 to što se zovem sanja.

971
01:01:05,580 --> 01:01:07,960
 Zato što si sanjala.

972
01:01:07,960 --> 01:01:09,020
 Tako je.

973
01:01:09,020 --> 01:01:11,480
 Moj sada i zato je došlo

974
01:01:11,480 --> 01:01:12,140
 i me sanja.

975
01:01:12,140 --> 01:01:14,480
 A zato je taj mala Terezija.

976
01:01:14,480 --> 01:01:16,560
 Gospodin s vama.

977
01:01:16,560 --> 01:01:18,020
 I s duham tvojim.

978
01:01:18,020 --> 01:01:19,880
 Neka vas blagoslovljeni čuva

979
01:01:19,880 --> 01:01:20,840
 svebogući Bog,

980
01:01:20,840 --> 01:01:21,840
 Otac i sin,

981
01:01:22,040 --> 01:01:22,960
 Edo sve ti.

982
01:01:22,960 --> 01:01:23,820
 Amen.

983
01:01:23,820 --> 01:01:24,340
 Amen.

